#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/code-of-conduct.md:70
msgid "Part 2.3 Consequences of Unacceptable behaviour"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/code-of-conduct.md:72
msgid ""
"Participants who are asked to stop any inappropriate behaviour are "
"expected to comply immediately. This applies to any Carpentries events "
"and platforms, either online or in-person. If a participant engages in "
"behaviour that violates this code of conduct, the organizers may warn the"
" offender, ask them to leave the event or platform (without refund), or "
"engage the Carpentries Code of Conduct Committee to investigate the Code "
"of Conduct violation and impose appropriate sanctions."
